ThinkPart(
    type='think',
    think='Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the PR. Let me compile my
findings and write the review report.\n\nKey issues to report:\n\n**Blocking Iss
ues:**\n1. **Race condition in CreateOrGetConversation** (`internal/data/wapi/im
.go:31-61`): Concurrent requests for the same participants can both query, both 
get NotFound, then both try to create. One succeeds, the other fails with unique
constraint violation. The error is returned directly to the caller. This breaks 
the "get or create" contract.\n   - Fix: Wrap the get+create in a transaction, o
r handle the unique constraint violation by re-querying.\n\n2. **MarkAsRead part
ial commit risk** (`internal/biz/wapi/im.go:273-324`): BatchCreateReadReceipts a
nd ClearUnreadCount are executed before GetMessagesByIDs. If the latter fails, p
artial state has been committed but an error is returned. This can lead to data 
inconsistency (read receipts created but WS notifications not sent, or unread co
unt cleared but error returned).\n   - Fix: Move GetMessagesByIDs before the wri
te operations, or wrap the writes in a transaction.\n\n**Major Issues:**\n1. **S
ceneSwitchBar uses magic numbers and export default** (`apps/phaser3/src/city-bu
